Build a production-quality local web application: a real-time Kubernetes/OpenShift log explorer designed specifically for fast live debugging sessions.

This is NOT an analytics platform and NOT a logging system.

This is a focused “Live Debug Console” for a single pod at a time.

The goal is:
👉 a developer should identify production issues in under 30 seconds.

---

🧱 Tech Stack (STRICT)

Frontend

- React (Vite)
- TypeScript
- TailwindCSS (clean modern UI only)
- shadcn/ui (ONLY for basic components)
- Zustand (single global state store)
- react-window (required for performance)
- WebSocket client

Backend

- Node.js (LTS)
- ws (WebSocket)
- child_process.spawn ("oc logs")
- Express (minimal API only)
- NO external services

