🧭 CORE USER FLOW (MANDATORY UX)

The UI must enforce this strict flow:

Step 1: Namespace select (dropdown)

Step 2: Deployment select (filtered dropdown)

Step 3: Pod select (filtered dropdown)

ONLY after this:
→ logs start streaming

❗ No manual typing of names
❗ No free text selection

---

🧠 CORE BEHAVIOR MODEL

SINGLE POD MODE (ABSOLUTE RULE)

- Only ONE pod can be active
- Switching pod:
  - clears UI instantly
  - stops previous stream
  - resets state
  - starts new stream

No multi-pod support.

