🧠 STREAMING BEHAVIOR (ANTI-CHAOS SYSTEM)

1. Smart auto-scroll

- only scroll if user is at bottom

2. Pause on scroll up

- user scrolls up → freeze view
- logs still collected

3. Batch rendering

- render logs every 100–200ms

---

4. Noise control (CRITICAL)

Deduplication:

- identical logs grouped:
  (×N) message

Burst grouping:

- collapse spikes into expandable group

Minimal UI noise rule:

- never spam UI with repeated logs

